<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4519091>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 10–16. Adults of Dargida phaeoneura comb. nov., in dorsal and ventral views. Figs 10–11. Male holotype (NH- MUK). Fig. 12. Male paralectotype of Borolia lillioana Köhler, 1947 (new synonym of D. phaeoneura) (ZSBS). Figs 13–14. Male from near Tafí del Valle, Tucumán, Argentina (CAL). Figs 15–16. Female from La Paz, Bolívia (IADIZA). Scale bar: 1cm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4519091/files/figure.png" .

